                  </hi>. I am a master, in a school. On 24th Aug. I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184809180176"></xptr>
               <p>felt a tug at my pocket, in the Waterloo-road, and saw the prisoner behind me with my handkerchief in his hand—this is it (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—he threw through an area-railing—I caught him—he struggled, and said he had not taken it—I took him to the area—he struck rue, and <hi rend="italic">bolted</hi> down a bye-street—he was stopped.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
