                        <interp inst="t18480918-name-875" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY STREET</persName>
                  </hi>, I am a porter, at the South Western Railway. I saw the prisoner running, and crying, "Stop thief!"—I followed him half a mile—he used great violence—I got assistance—he said there were no d----d companions, or else they would rescue him from me—I gave him in charge.</p>
